for _ in range(int(input())):
    (N, X) = map(int, input().split())
    A = list(map(int, input().split()))
    print('YES' if X <= max(A) else 'NO')

t = int(input())
for _ in range(t):
    line = input().split()
    n = int(line[0])
    x = int(line[1])
    students = list(map(int, input().split()))
    n_valid = len(list(filter(lambda s: s >= x, students)))
    if n_valid == 0:
        print('NO')
    else:
        print('YES')
